that period of time.

00:00:54.817 --> 00:00:55.650 align:middle line:90%
>>JOHN PERKINS: Yes.

00:00:55.650 --> 00:00:57.080 align:middle line:84%
It's great to be
with you, Regina,

00:00:57.080 --> 00:00:59.530 align:middle line:84%
