00:01:19.800 --> 00:01:22.240 align:middle line:84%
So let's just take a moment
and roll that animation.

00:01:22.240 --> 00:01:23.859 align:middle line:90%
>>PERKINS: OK.

00:01:23.859 --> 00:01:24.525 align:middle line:90%
