00:01:24.525 --> 00:01:27.100 align:middle line:84%
We economic hitmen have
managed to create the world's

00:01:27.100 --> 00:01:30.260 align:middle line:84%
first truly global empire, and
it's basically a secret empire.

00:01:30.260 --> 00:01:31.210 align:middle line:90%
We do it in many ways.

00:01:31.210 --> 00:01:34.120 align:middle line:10%
But principally, we
identify a country

00:01:34.120 --> 00:01:36.910 align:middle line:10%
that has resources our
corporations covet, like oil,

00:01:36.910 --> 00:01:39.210 align:middle line:10%
arrange a huge loan to that
country from the World Bank

00:01:39.210 --> 00:01:40.345 align:middle line:10%
or one of its sisters.

00:01:40.345 --> 00:01:42.220 align:middle line:10%
The money never actually
goes to the country.

00:01:42.220 --> 00:01:44.840 align:middle line:10%
It goes to our own corporations
to build the infrastructure

00:01:44.840 --> 00:01:48.990 align:middle line:10%
projects in that country that
help a few very wealthy people,

00:01:48.990 --> 00:01:50.990 align:middle line:10%
but don't benefit the
majority of the people who

00:01:50.990 --> 00:01:53.100 align:middle line:10%
are too poor to buy
electricity or have

00:01:53.100 --> 00:01:54.950 align:middle line:10%
cars to drive on the highways.

00:01:54.950 --> 00:01:56.860 align:middle line:84%
And yet, they're left
holding a huge debt

00:01:56.860 --> 00:01:58.630 align:middle line:90%
that they can't repay.

00:01:58.630 --> 00:02:02.269 align:middle line:84%
So we go back at some point and
say, you can't pay your debts.

00:02:02.269 --> 00:02:03.310 align:middle line:10%
Give us a pound of flesh.

00:02:03.310 --> 00:02:06.680 align:middle line:10%
Sell your oil real cheap
to our oil companies.

00:02:06.680 --> 00:02:09.150 align:middle line:10%
Vote with us on the
next critical UN vote.

00:02:09.150 --> 00:02:13.634 align:middle line:10%
Allow us to build a military
base in your backyard.

00:02:13.634 --> 00:02:14.800 align:middle line:10%
Something along these lines.

00:02:14.800 --> 00:02:17.550 align:middle line:10%
And when we fail, the
jackals go in and either

00:02:17.550 --> 00:02:20.820 align:middle line:10%
