these leaders.

00:02:20.820 --> 00:02:23.855 align:middle line:10%
And if the jackals fail,
as they did in Iraq, then

00:02:23.855 --> 00:02:25.690 align:middle line:10%
we send in the military.

00:02:25.690 --> 00:02:27.660 align:middle line:10%
I don't think the
failure is capitalism.

00:02:27.660 --> 00:02:30.546 align:middle line:10%
I think it's a specific
kind of capitalism where

00:02:30.546 --> 00:02:33.260 align:middle line:10%
we've developed-- we've
created what I consider

00:02:33.260 --> 00:02:37.190 align:middle line:10%
a mutant viral
form of capitalism.

00:02:37.190 --> 00:02:39.070 align:middle line:84%
And this mutant
form of capitalism,

00:02:39.070 --> 00:02:42.680 align:middle line:84%
which I think is really a
predatory form of capitalism,

00:02:42.680 --> 00:02:46.350 align:middle line:84%
has created an extremely
unstable, unsustainable,

00:02:46.350 --> 00:02:48.950 align:middle line:84%
unjust, and very,
very dangerous world.

00:02:48.950 --> 00:02:50.890 align:middle line:90%
