00:03:02.170 --> 00:03:03.860 align:middle line:10%
If we want to get
rid of terrorism,

00:03:03.860 --> 00:03:07.670 align:middle line:10%
we must get rid of the root
causes, that cancer that

00:03:07.670 --> 00:03:10.137 align:middle line:10%
is destroying our whole system.

00:03:10.137 --> 00:03:12.470 align:middle line:10%
Because I think it's really
important that we understand

00:03:12.470 --> 00:03:16.120 align:middle line:10%
