Increasing steel
prices by some $6 a ton

00:34:16.580 --> 00:34:21.600 align:middle line:84%
constitute a wholly unjustified
and irresponsible defiance

00:34:21.600 --> 00:34:22.690 align:middle line:90%
of the public interest.

00:34:22.690 --> 00:34:23.219 align:middle line:90%
